rilsk]]) ('''1''')\n|[[MFK GKI-Gazprom Moskva|GKI-Gazprom]] (Moscow)\n|[[MFK Spartak Moskva|Spartak]] (Moscow)\n|-\n|[[2002\u201303 Russian Futsal Super League|2002-03]]\n|'''[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo]] '''(Moscow)\n|[[MFK Norilsk Nickel|Norilsky Nikel]] (Norilsk)\n|[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekaterinburg|VIZ-Sinara]] (Yekaterinburg)\n|-\n|[[2003\u201304 Russian Futsal Super League|2003-04]]\n|'''[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo]] '''(Moscow)\n|[[MFK Dina Moskva|Dina]] (Moscow)\n|[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekaterinburg|VIZ-Sinara]] (Yekaterinburg)\n|-\n|[[2004\u201305 Russian Futsal Super League|2004-05]]\n|'''[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo]] '''(Moscow)\n|[[MFK Spartak-Shchyolkovo|Spartak-Shchyolkovo]] ([[Moscow Oblast]])\n|[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekaterinburg|VIZ-Sinara]] (Yekaterinburg)\n|-\n|[[2005\u201306 Russian Futsal Super League|2005-06]]\n|'''[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo]] '''(Moscow)\n|[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekaterinburg|VIZ-Sinara]] (Yekaterinburg)\n|[[MFK Spartak-Shchyolkovo|Spartak-Shchyolkovo]] (Moscow Oblast)\n|-\n|[[2006\u201307 Russian Futsal Super League|2006-07]]\n|'''[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo]] '''(Moscow)\n|[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekaterinburg|VIZ-Sinara]] (Yekaterinburg)\n|[[MFK TTG-Java Yugorsk|TTG-Java]] (Yugorsk)\n|-\n|[[2007\u201308 Russian Futsal Super League|2007-08]]\n|'''[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo-Yamal]] '''(Moscow)\n|[[MFK TTG-Java Yugorsk|TTG-Java]] (Yugorsk)\n|[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekaterinburg|VIZ-Sinara]] (Yekaterinburg)\n|-\n|[[2008\u201309 Russian Futsal Super League|2008-09]]\n|'''[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekaterinburg|VIZ-Sinara]] '''(Yekaterinburg)\n|[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo-Yamal]] (Moscow)\n|[[MFK TTG-Yugra Yugorsk|TTG-Yugra]] (Yugorsk)\n|-\n|[[2009\u201310 Russian Futsal Super League|2009-10]]\n|'''[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekaterinburg|VIZ-Sinara]]''' (Yekaterinburg) ('''2''')\n|[[MFK Tyumen|Tyumen]] (Tyumen)\n|[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo-Yamal]] (Moscow)\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 Russian Futsal Super League|2010-11]]\n|'''[[MFK Dinamo Moskva|Dinamo Moscow]]'''\n|[[MFK VIZ-Sinara Yekateri